question: Do you know any forts that are within 20km of Tanglin?
query:
PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q7683056" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:historic "fort" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) <= 20000)
}

PREFIX geof: <http://www.opengis.net/def/function/geosparql/>
PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q13882341" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:building "university" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    BIND(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) AS ?distance)
}
ORDER BY ASC(?distance)
LIMIT 1

PREFIX osmkey: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:>
PREFIX osm: <https://www.openstreetmap.org/>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX uom: <http://www.opengis.net/def/uom/OGC/1.0/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?class WHERE {
    ?region1 osmkey:wikidata "Q16887503" .
    ?region1 geo:hasGeometry ?rwkt1 .
    ?class osmkey:waterway "dam" .
    ?class geo:hasGeometry ?cwkt1 .
    FILTER(geof:distance(?rwkt1,?cwkt1,uom:metre) > 5000)
}

question: What are the names of the forest and river in Potong Pasir?

}
